OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778410973
OL,3,CMan in court over attempted PSNI
OL,4,Cstation bombing
OL,6,FA 47-year-old man has appeared in
OL,7,Fcourt charged with attempted murder
OL,8,Fover an attempted car bomb attack on
OL,9,FLurgan PSNI station.
OL,11,FThe New IRA claimed responsibility for
OL,12,Fthe incident that saw a pizza delivery
OL,13,Fdriver hijacked in Kilwilkie and
OL,14,Fforced to drive a pipe bomb to the
OL,15,Fstation on the night of March 30.
OL,17,FThe device did not explode but was
OL,18,Fdeemed to be viable, before being made
OL,19,Fsafe and being tested for forensics.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778410973
OL,3,CMan in court over attempted PSNI
OL,4,Cstation bombing
OL,6,FBarry Anthony Toman, with an address
OL,7,Fat Drumnamoe Avenue in Lurgan,
OL,8,Fappeared before Craigavon Magistrates'
OL,9,FCourt via videolink on Friday.
OL,11,FThe court was told his DNA could be
OL,12,Ffound on five different parts of the
OL,13,Fbomb.
OL,15,FToman was charged with attempted
OL,16,Fmurder, an attempt to cause an
OL,17,Fexplosion, and hijacking by compelling
OL,18,Fa person to drive a car carrying an
OL,19,Fimprovised explosive device relating
OL,20,Fto the attack near Lurgan PSNI station.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778410973
OL,3,CMan in court over attempted PSNI
OL,4,Cstation bombing
OL,6,FHe was also charged with possession of
OL,7,Fexplosives with intent to endanger
OL,8,Flife on a date before March 31.
OL,10,FHe was one of three people arrested on
OL,11,FWednesday by police investigating the
OL,12,Fincident.
OL,14,FIn court on Friday, he spoke only to
OL,15,Fconfirm he understood the charges
OL,16,Fagainst him.
OL,18,FA Detective Chief Inspector with the
OL,19,FPSNI said he could connect the accused
OL,20,Fto the charges as he outlined DNA,
OL,21,FCCTV, and phone evidence to the court.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778410973
OL,3,CMan in court over attempted PSNI
OL,4,Cstation bombing
OL,6,FThe DCI explained that, on the night
OL,7,Fin question, a pizza delivery driver
OL,8,Fwas responding to an order made over
OL,9,Fphone with the cost to be paid on
OL,10,Fdelivery.
OL,12,FThe address on the delivery was at the
OL,13,Ftop end of an alleyway, with the
OL,14,Foccupants of the house later telling
OL,15,Fpolice they did not make the order.
OL,17,FThe DCI said Toman's home address was
OL,18,Fon the 200-metre long alleyway.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778410973
OL,3,CMan in court over attempted PSNI
OL,4,Cstation bombing
OL,6,FHe said CCTV showed two people
OL,7,Femerging before making demands and
OL,8,Fphysically ushering the driver into
OL,9,Fthe alleyway.
OL,11,FPolice assert that one of the people,
OL,12,Fa male, primed the bomb and placed it
OL,13,Finto the boot of the driver's car
OL,14,Fbefore a second male brings the
OL,15,Fdelivery driver back to the car door
OL,16,Fand makes threatening motion.
OL,18,FThe DCI said the driver drove the bomb
OL,19,Fto the front gate of Lurgan PSNI
OL,20,Fstation under instruction, where he
OL,21,Ftold the police about the bomb.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778410973
OL,3,CMan in court over attempted PSNI
OL,4,Cstation bombing
OL,6,FThe court heard specifics on how the
OL,7,Fthe timing device was intended to
OL,8,Fdetonate the bomb, which was described
OL,9,Fas a timed pipe bomb containing
OL,10,Fexplosives and shrapnel surrounded by
OL,11,Fjars of flammable liquid to "create
OL,12,Fmaximum fire damage".
OL,14,FThe area around the station was
OL,15,Fcordoned off and nearby premises were
OL,16,Fevacuated before army technical
OL,17,Fofficers were called to the scene.
OL,26,@sD@]OUtD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778410973
OL,3,CMan in court over attempted PSNI
OL,4,Cstation bombing
OL,6,FThe DCI said DNA matching Toman was
OL,7,Ffound on five locations on the device
OL,8,Fincluding the edge of a battery
OL,9,Fcompartment, an AA battery that was
OL,10,Ffound in the boot that was believed to
OL,11,Fhave been in the bomb, a piece of tape
OL,12,Fholding wires, and on a screw.
OL,14,FThe court heard that over the course
OL,15,Fof more than five hours across nine
OL,16,Fpolice interviews, Toman did not
OL,17,Fprovide any comment to questions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778410973
OL,3,CMan in court over attempted PSNI
OL,4,Cstation bombing
OL,6,FHowever, after being presented with
OL,7,Fthe DNA evidence, he provided a
OL,8,Fprepared statement in which he
OL,9,Fexplained he had worked on
OL,10,Fconstruction sites and public places
OL,11,Fwhere he had been in constant contact
OL,12,Fwith screws, batteries and other tools.
OL,14,FThe DCI said he did not answer further
OL,15,Fquestions relating to this.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778410973
OL,3,CMan in court over attempted PSNI
OL,4,Cstation bombing
OL,6,FThe PSNI representative said a phone
OL,7,Fpresent on Toman at the time of his
OL,8,Farrest did not have any device
OL,9,Fcommands recorded before April 5,
OL,10,Fwhich he said suggested a physical act
OL,11,Fto delete the information.
OL,13,FThe DCI also said his home address,
OL,14,Fthe area where the attack happened,
OL,15,Fand the area the pizza delivery order
OL,16,Fwas made were all contained within the
OL,17,Fsame phone cell area.
OL,19,FHe said the phone used to make the
OL,20,Forder was a prepay no-details held
OL,21,Fphone.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778410973
OL,3,CMan in court over attempted PSNI
OL,4,Cstation bombing
OL,6,FThe DCI said a 15-year-old had paid
OL,7,Ffor a relevant top-up for that phone
OL,8,Fwith a #20 note and a file had been
OL,9,Fprepared for the Public Prosecution
OL,10,FService.
OL,12,FThe PSNI said there was a photo on
OL,13,FToman's phone of a #20 note and a #10
OL,14,Fnote approximately two hours before
OL,15,Fthat top up.
OL,17,FThe DCI told the court it was the
OL,18,FPSNI's belief the accused was a "a
OL,19,Fcommitted violent terrorist".
OL,26,@zD@aOU{D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778410973
OL,3,CMan in court over attempted PSNI
OL,4,Cstation bombing
OL,6,FUnder questioning from Toman's
OL,7,Fsolicitor Gavin Booth, the DCI said
OL,8,Fthe CCTV was not good enough to make
OL,9,Fout who the men were and was not
OL,10,Fcurrently enough to identify the
OL,11,Faccused.
OL,13,FThe DCI also accepted the cell-site
OL,14,Fanalysis could not triangulate the
OL,15,Fcalls to a single person or location.
OL,17,FHe said there was "nothing at this
OL,18,Fstage" to link Toman to the phone used
OL,19,Fto contact the delivery order.
OL,26,@yD@SOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778410973
OL,3,CMan in court over attempted PSNI
OL,4,Cstation bombing
OL,6,FUnder further questioning by Mr Booth,
OL,7,Fhe said the "preliminary" DNA evidence
OL,8,Fwas made up of one partial sample and
OL,9,Fa number of mixed samples.
OL,11,FHe accepted that it could not be used
OL,12,Fto determine who was the last person
OL,13,Fto touch an object.
OL,15,FThe DCI said in one of the mixed
OL,16,Fsamples it meant he was one of two
OL,17,Fpeople to touch the object.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778410973
OL,3,CMan in court over attempted PSNI
OL,4,Cstation bombing
OL,6,FHe added that in the partial sample,
OL,7,Fthe likelihood of it being someone
OL,8,Fother than Toman was "a billion to
OL,9,Fone".
OL,11,FThe court also heard that DNA can be
OL,12,Ftransferred from one location to
OL,13,Fanother.
OL,15,FThe magistrate said he was satisfied
OL,16,Fthe PSNI had sufficient evidence to
OL,17,Fproperly connect the accused to the
OL,18,Foffending
OL,20,FThere was no bail application at the
OL,21,Fhearing and legal aid was granted.
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778410973
OL,3,CMan in court over attempted PSNI
OL,4,Cstation bombing
OL,6,FThe matter will return before the
OL,7,Fcourts on June 5.
OL,9,FElsewhere, a 39-year-old woman has
OL,10,Fbeen charged with obstructing police
OL,11,Fin relation to the incident.
OL,13,FShe has been released unconditionally
OL,14,Fin respect of perverting the course of
OL,15,Fjustice and assisting an offender.
OL,17,FShe is expected to appear before
OL,18,FCraigavon Magistrates' Court on June 3.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
